Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.63,0:02:39.39,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\1a&HFF&\blur8}漕いで行く　漕いで行く
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.39,0:02:41.72,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\1a&HFF&\blur8}どこへ行こう
